These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, collecting
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike
1. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | collecting | card-games |
| Transport     | motorbike    | airplane   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk
City: san-francisco, hamburg
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee        |
| City      | san-francisco  | hamburg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, house
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, tulip
1. the person who growslily is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | house    | ambient |
| Flower   | lily | tulip |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade
2 different pets are kept: bird, fish
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the owner of the fish is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | 7up      | lemonade |
| Pet       | bird | fish    |

